":"1224","julianDay":2168117,"title":"France Declares War on England","description":"France declared war on England as Louis VIII of France attacked Poitou and northern Gascony.","jurisdictionLevel":1}],"lifeSummary":"Mabel was born in 1124, in Lancashire, England. She had at least 1 son with Roger de Montbegon III. She died in England, United Kingdom."},"et":{"1124–":"1124–Surnud","1090–1149":"1090–1149","1140–1181":"1140–1181","1124–Female":"1124–Surnud","about 1140":"umbes 1140","1090":"1090","1215":"1215","1149":"1149","1224":"1224","1124":"1124","1140":"1140","1181":"1181","England":"Inglismaa, United Kingdom","Lancashire, England":"Lancashire, England","Hornby Castle, Lancashire, England":"Hornby Castle, Lancashire, England"},"fi":{"1124–":"1124–Kuollut","1090–1149":"1090–1149","1140–1181":"1140–1181","1124–Female":"1124–Kuollut","about 1140":"noin 1140","1090":"1090","1215":"1215","1149":"1149","1224":"1224","1124":"1124","1140":"1140","1181":"1181","England":"Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta","Lancashire, England":"Lancashire, England","Hornby Castle, Lancashire, England":"Hornby Castle, Lancashire, England"},"fr":{"1124–":"1124–Décédée","1090–1149":"1090–1149","1140–1181":"1140–1181","1124–Female":"1124–Décédée","about 1140":"environ 1140","1090":"1090","1215":"1215","1149":"1149","1224":"1224","1124":"1124","1140":"1140","1181":"1181","England":"Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","Lancashire, England":"Lancashire, Angleterre","Hornby Castle, Lancashire, England":"Hornby Castle, Lancashire, Angleterre","lifeSummary":"Mabel est née en 1124, à Lancashire, Angleterre. Elle a eu au moins 1 fils avec Roger de Montbegon III. Elle est décédée à Angleterre, Royaume-Uni."},"de":{"1124–":"1124–Verstorben","1090–1149":"1090–1149","1140–1181":"1140–1181","1124–Female":"1124–Verstorben","about 1140":"um 1140","1090":"1090","1215":"1215","1149":"1149","1224":"1224","1124":"1124","1140":"1140","1181":"1181","England":"England, United Kingdom","Lancashire, England":"Lancashire, En